# Changelog
All notable changes to this program 'reverseTranslate' will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.0] - 2021-12-09
### Added 
- Removal of empty lines in input files
- Modificated header at each output will print identification code insted of whole header line. 
- Program execution example is inserted in the program. 

### Fixed
- Subroutine problem with perlcritic was fixed by passing list @_ variable. 
- Due to percritic error with special symbols, line counting was substituted with header printing. 

### Changed
- Program specification file, new information added.
- Warning message format changed, insted of printing line number, header is printed. 
- Warning messages for empty sequence is changed.

## [0.1.0] - 2021-12-06
### Added 
- Program 'reverseTranslate'.
